		</Group>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水召唤的天蓝色史莱姆，其周期性喷吐疗愈晶球，晶球追踪无相之水，其治疗量对于角色为<span color="#7fbfff">50%生命值上限</span><span>，对于无相之水为</span><span color="#7fbfff">10%生命值上限</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="442" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水在空中翻涌，顷刻便扎入地里，造成<span color="#7fbfff">33.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。施放该技能后的25s内，场地将随机出现成对的水泡，触碰造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水生命值低于5%时进行复苏，复苏持续20s，复苏时汇聚的水泡爆炸无伤害，爆炸召唤<span textDecoration="underline">濒死水滴</span><span>，水滴落地时造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，每个水滴恢复无相之水</span><span color="#7fbfff">15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水从场地边缘唤出8个水轴，其不断朝中央滚动，每个水轴触碰造成<span color="#7fbfff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，水轴最后漏入中心，引起水爆，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水化为高速旋转的水龙卷，预判玩家并在其下方生成3片雨区，每片雨区持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">33.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水幻化成群鱼，从远处下潜跃出命中玩家，造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，不暴露核心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1390" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="1034">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1392" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1392" y="809">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_19.png')" x="719" y="810">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_20.png')" x="719" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1392" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="432" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水挤压并汇聚水泡，随后水泡爆炸造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，爆炸召唤内鬼水滴和愈疗水滴，水滴着陆造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1409" y="447" width="437" height="115" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水幻化成鳐形，向玩家处拍击，同时产生1个方向的水喷，水喷和拍击均造成<span color="#7fbfff">66.6</span><span fontSize="25" color="#7fbfff">%,33.3%,16.6%,6.66%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="353" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">内鬼水滴：<span color="#7fbfff">2水</span><span>盾，击破即击败水滴，靠近即自爆。<br/>愈疗水滴：</span><span color="#7fbfff">2水</span><span>盾，击破即击败水滴。<br/>濒死水滴：</span><span color="#7fbfff">2水</span><span>盾，全部击破阻止无相之水复苏。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="421" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水汇聚水泡，随后破裂造成<span color="#7fbfff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，并暴露核心，同时在场地内召唤跃腾的海豚，海豚跃出造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，跃入造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">16.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之水.assets/Image_22.png')" x="720" y="1033">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之水召唤的深蓝色史莱姆，其始终追踪玩家，靠近时爆炸造成无相之水的<span color="#7fbfff">31.1%</span><span>伤害，若爆炸命中无相之水则强制暴露其核心一段时间。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
